original_title: Fly Filmmaking Challenge 2014: Seattle, I Love You
overview: This year, the Seattle International Film Festival (SIFF) challenged five local production companies to create a love letter to Seattle in a compilation affectionately titled, 'Seattle, I Love You'.  The five shorts within this omnibus production are: Sea Folk, Fresh Pair, Open Mouth, Hannah & Otto, Secret.
title: Fly Filmmaking Challenge 2014: Seattle, I Love You
